stories.text:
If the following book were written, would you care? Would you share? Save me from a herculean thankless task with your indifference, or hurl me into the abyss with your prospective interest.

Title

Moonshots: Ambitious Technology Development - A Book of Methods Developed in the Trenches.

Sample Contents: Introduction: The case for Ambitions Technology Development & Productive vs Creative Work. Part I: Methods for Individuals - How to organize your work, your day and your mind to maximize the chance of breakthrough. Part II: Methods for Teams and Managers - How to organize a team, and a team's work to maximize the chance of breakthrough. Part III: Methods for Portfolio Managers and Heads of R&D - How to Assess Investment, resource allocation and progress in the absence of predictable progress and traditional KPI's.
